title: Groove Armada takeover Pete Tong Essential Selection 20/03/2009
description:
Groove Armada takeover for Pete Tong Essential Selection
Friday 20th March 2009

Pete is away at SXSW this week so Andy and Tom from Groove Armada officially start the weekend!
 
Bringing with them loads of new tunes and some hot mixes from the boys themselves...

As well as chatting to Yousef and Ashley Beedle...

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, International
